OL,3,CNew DIY heart monitor hopes to speed
OL,4,Cup diagnosis
OL,6,FPatients across parts of Surrey and
OL,7,FBerkshire are the first in the country
OL,8,Fto benefit from a new heart monitor
OL,9,Fwhich detects rhythm problems.
OL,11,FThe device is smaller than traditional
OL,12,Fequipment and can be fitted at home,
OL,13,Fmeaning most patients don't have to
OL,14,Fwait for a hospital appointment.
OL,16,FFrimley Health NHS Foundation Trust
OL,17,Fhopes the technology will speed up
OL,18,Fdiagnosis.
