OL,3,CNew DIY heart monitor hopes to speed
OL,4,Cup diagnosis
OL,6,FMichael Howell is among the first
OL,7,Fpatients to have one of the monitors
OL,8,Ffitted, so that doctors can check
OL,9,Fwhether his heart is at risk ahead of
OL,10,Fan operation. It's the first of its
OL,11,Fkind to be used by the NHS.
OL,13,F"Very impressed actually, it's so
OL,14,Fsimple, I didn't realise it was going
OL,15,Fto be that easy.
OL,17,F"It's the first time I've had one, I
OL,18,Fdon't even know I've got it on;
OL,19,Fseriously, I don't, it feels really
OL,20,Fgood."
