OL,3,CNew DIY heart monitor hopes to speed
OL,4,Cup diagnosis
OL,6,FAnother patient, Linda Payne, said: "I
OL,7,Fwasn't prepared for that to be quite
OL,8,Fso quick and easy. When he put it on I
OL,9,Fwas expecting far more but there's
OL,10,Fnothing to it."
OL,12,FA small patch carrying the device is
OL,13,Fstuck to the centre of the chest. It's
OL,14,Fthen worn for five days, constantly
OL,15,Frecording the patient's heart rhythm
OL,16,Fby collecting electrical signals.
