OL,3,CNew DIY heart monitor hopes to speed
OL,4,Cup diagnosis
OL,6,FAssociate Cardiac Physiologist, Andrew
OL,7,FGreen said: "From a patient's point of
OL,8,Fview it's more hygienic because they
OL,9,Fcan obviously change the sticker if
OL,10,Fthey need to, throw it in the bin.
OL,11,FThey can shower with it.
OL,13,F"With the old ones, they've obviously
OL,14,Fgot cables and they have to tuck them
OL,15,Fdown their trousers or somewhere else
OL,16,Fso I think the patches are better.
OL,18,F"The fitting of it is quicker, we can
OL,19,Fdo probably twice as many patients in
OL,20,Fa day as what we were doing before."
