OL,3,CNew DIY heart monitor hopes to speed
OL,4,Cup diagnosis
OL,6,FThe new kit can be used to investigate
OL,7,Firregular heartbeats which can be
OL,8,Fcaused by a number of heart conditions.
OL,10,FConsultant Cardiologist, Dr Mark
OL,11,FNorman said: "Palpitations will be how
OL,12,Fa patient might present to a GP.
OL,13,FSeventy per cent of people with
OL,14,Fpalpitations have a normal rhythm.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
