OL,3,CNew DIY heart monitor hopes to speed
OL,4,Cup diagnosis
OL,6,F"Disturbance of rhythm is called
OL,7,Fdysrhythmia and so it will firstly
OL,8,Fclarify that and secondly clarify, if
OL,9,Fyou have a dysrhythmia, does it come
OL,10,Ffrom; the atrium, the small chamber of
OL,11,Fthe heart, or the big chamber of the
OL,12,Fheart, the engine, the ventricle.
OL,14,F"Then from there you can then
OL,15,Fsubclassify each of the arrhythmias
OL,16,Fbased on the electrical signal that
OL,17,Fyou get from the monitor."
