OL,3,CNew DIY heart monitor hopes to speed
OL,4,Cup diagnosis
OL,6,FThe device can also be sent in the
OL,7,Fpost, saving a trip to hospital, and
OL,8,Fpatients can fit it themselves in the
OL,9,Fcomfort of their own home.
OL,11,FThe results are first assessed by
OL,12,Fartificial intelligence before being
OL,13,Fanalysed by a doctor.
OL,15,FIt's hoped the technology will soon be
OL,16,Frolled out across the country to speed
OL,17,Fup diagnoses.
